00:26:09.120 --> 00:26:11.580
Dia seperti muncul entah dari mana.

00:26:13.880 --> 00:26:14.970
Sememangnya, dia bukan manusia biasa.

00:26:16.070 --> 00:26:16.620
Walau bagaimanapun,

00:26:17.990 --> 00:26:19.420
jika dia bukan salah seorang pengikut Marquis of Nanyan,

00:26:20.990 --> 00:26:22.530
kenapa dia muncul di sebelah saya?

00:26:24.960 --> 00:26:25.940
Apa yang dia buat?

00:26:27.710 --> 00:26:28.970
Puan, adakah anda berkata

00:26:30.120 --> 00:26:33.860
