00:28:06.470 --> 00:28:07.580
Puan, tolong jangan tolak kami.

00:28:07.880 --> 00:28:09.860
Lebih baik selamat daripada menyesal.

00:28:10.790 --> 00:28:11.490
Pakar Perubatan Imperial Yi.

00:28:16.960 --> 00:28:18.290
Salam, Puan.

